# Docker build context exclusions.
#
# Caught 2026-05-09: a stale ``src/audittrace_ai.egg-info`` from a
# developer's local ``pip install -e .`` got baked into the v1.0.13
# image because there was no .dockerignore. The frozen
# ``Version: 1.0.11`` in the egg-info's PKG-INFO won the
# ``importlib.metadata.version("audittrace-ai")`` lookup at runtime,
# so the deployed v1.0.13 pod self-identified to /health (and Tempo,
# and Langfuse) as v1.0.11. Twelve previous releases shipped with
# whatever stale metadata happened to be on the maintainer's laptop
# at build time — same drift class as the OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES
# service.version=1.0.0 freeze.
#
# Conservative posture: exclude only build artefacts, virtual envs,
# IDE noise, and secrets. Keep tests/, charts/, docs/ in the context
# because the multi-stage Dockerfile's Stage 3 (tests image) COPY's
# them in. Excluding them at the .dockerignore level breaks the
# in-cluster integration-test image build.

# ── Python build / install metadata ──────────────────────────────────
**/*.egg-info/
**/*.egg
**/*.dist-info
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/htmlcov/
**/.coverage
**/coverage.xml
**/junit.xml

# ── Virtual environments ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
venv/
env/

# ── Editor / IDE / OS noise ──────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Git metadata (Docker build doesn't need it) ──────────────────────
.git/

# ── Local secrets (defence in depth — never in image) ────────────────
secrets/*
!secrets/.gitkeep
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Build / deployment artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.bak
*.tmp
node_modules/
